-- Beazer says bankruptcy rumors are unfounded
-- 
-- Wed Aug 1, 2007 12:33pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/08/01/us-beazer-rumors-idUSWNAS923420070801

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Beazer Homes USA Inc. ( BZH.N ) said on Wednesday that rumors it would soon be filing for bankruptcy protection were unfounded. 

 "We have become aware of rumors circulating in the market about Beazer Homes' liquidity and a prospective bankruptcy filing. We do not know where these scurrilous and unfounded rumors started," the company said in a statement. "For an accurate representation of the company's financial position, including the company's liquidity and near-term prospects, we encourage investors to refer to the company's recently released third-quarter earnings release and the script of our conference call with analysts and investors," the company said.